# Rules for AI Agents in this Repository (Cursor)

⚠️ This file is a pointer. Canonical rules live in AGENTS.md and ONBOARDING.md.

Before any Edit / Write / Bash operation, you MUST read:

1. ONBOARDING.md — 3-layer load strategy (Must-read / Boot ritual / On-demand)
2. AGENTS.md — 11 global hard rules (Git pre-flight #13, irreversible-ops ban #11, AI-driven business must feature-log #9, archive immutability #10, etc.)
3. CLAUDE.md — runtime SOP + Skill 速查 + mechanical checks index

